{
  "stem": "11167.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It wasn't a easy thing to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We did register.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because I did work in this [INAUDIBLE], I did get paid.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I bought a lot of things for Israel-- prepared myself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I bought pots, and I bought, everything what you need for a kitchen sink, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a lot to-- to take.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A lot of things if you only had money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One thing that I forgot to tell you, when I came to Wetzlar, and I did see in the window, was the soap, from Juden fats.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The soap made from Juden fats.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Wetzlar.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we came in to Wetzlar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The shop window.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fat-- soap made out of Jewish fat on sale in a window in--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in the windows.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They still didn't manage to-- to clear it up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was-- that was the good one, things already.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to surround our-- you know, the camps-- the DP camps.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They used to surround with wire.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Three times a week.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Something did happen, straight away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Straight away, they used to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We couldn't get out, we couldn't get in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that was nothing to compare with all the-- the difficulties, what I went through.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was really like to eat the ice cream, is nothing, to-- to compare what I went through.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then when Israel was declared, we had a very big-- not a party, all the 1,500 people was congregated in a-- in a place, and with speakers from Israel, with speakers from all over [? there. ?] A lot of people came.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And one thing what they did ask us, don't go to any country.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We need you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We need you people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We need you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A lot of people couldn't wait, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
